{
  "page": "Tumberjon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Tumberjon</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Tumberjon</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Ranger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ranger\">ranger</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tumberjon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tumberjon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Tumberjon is part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_ranging\" title=\"Great ranging\">great ranging</a> that leaves <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a> to search for <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a>. He is one of the scouts commanded by <a href=\"/index.php/Thoren_Smallwood\" title=\"Thoren Smallwood\">Thoren Smallwood</a> who are sent up the <a href=\"/index.php/Frostfangs\" title=\"Frostfangs\">Frostfangs</a> to find the wildlings. Tumberjon wants to put an arrow into <a href=\"/index.php/Harma\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Harma\">Harma the Dogshead</a>, but is ordered not to by Thoren.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Tumberjon possibly returns to Castle Black and then departs with <a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a> to confront the <a href=\"/index.php/Weeper\" title=\"Weeper\">Weeper</a>. The brothers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> left to defend the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">the wildling assault</a> name straw dummies after missing brothers, including <a href=\"/index.php/Eddison_Tollett\" title=\"Eddison Tollett\">Eddison Tollett</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Othell_Yarwyck\" title=\"Othell Yarwyck\">Othell Yarwyck</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Watt_of_Long_Lake\" title=\"Watt of Long Lake\">Watt of Long Lake</a>, and Tumberjon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tumberjon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Harma\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Harma\">Harma the Dogshead</a> has the van, the poxy bitch. <a href=\"/index.php/Goady\" title=\"Goady\">Goady</a> crept up on her camp and saw her plain by the fire. That fool Tumberjon wanted to pick her off with an arrow, but <a href=\"/index.php/Thoren_Smallwood\" title=\"Thoren Smallwood\">Smallwood</a> had better sense.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Kedge_Whiteye\" title=\"Kedge Whiteye\">Kedge Whiteye</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Chett\" title=\"Chett\">Chett</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tumberjon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Prologue\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink